cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques to improve the recognition of spatiotemporal expressions. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves active learning and ensemble methods, which are commonly used in information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE).
